(184, 1, '2023-03-30 12:35:36', '2023-03-30 12:35:36', '\"MS Dhoni: The Untold Story\" is a biographical film based on the life of Indian cricketer Mahendra Singh Dhoni. The film was directed by Neeraj Pandey and produced by Fox Star Studios. The movie features Sushant Singh Rajput in the lead role, portraying the character of Mahendra Singh Dhoni.\r\n\r\nThe movie showcases Dhoni\'s journey from a small town boy to becoming the captain of the Indian cricket team and leading the team to win the 2007 ICC World Twenty20, the 2010 and 2016 Asia Cups, and the 2011 ICC Cricket World Cup. The film also depicts Dhoni\'s personal life, including his relationships with his family, friends, and teammates.\r\n\r\n\"MS Dhoni: The Untold Story\" was released in 2016 and was a critical and commercial success. The movie was praised for its performances, direction, and screenplay, and was one of the highest-grossing movies of that year in India. The film also won several awards, including three National Film Awards.\r\n\r\n[foogallery id=\"185\"]', 'Ms Dhoni-The untold story', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ms-dhoni-the-untold-story', '', '', '2023-03-30 12:35:58', '2023-03-30 12:35:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress3/?post_type=movie&#038;p=184', 0, 'movie', '', 0),
